<div dir="ltr"><div>Some more info:</div><div> </div><div>The MOFED that you will download will have MXM in it, but it is an older version of it (v1.1). A new version of MXM (v1.5) is available.</div><div> </div><div>So, after installing MOFED, please erase the MXM in it (rpm -e mxm) and download the new MXM (v1.5) from:</div>
<div><a href="http://www.mellanox.com/page/products_dyn?product_family=135&amp;mtag=mxm">http://www.mellanox.com/page/products_dyn?product_family=135&amp;mtag=mxm</a></div><div>(the one that matches your OS)</div><div> </div>
<div>Thanks,</div><div>Alina</div></div><div class="gmail_extra"><br><br><div class="gmail_quote">On Wed, Jan 23, 2013 at 11:28 AM, Alina Sklarevich <span dir="ltr">&lt;<a href="mailto:alinas@dev.mellanox.co.il" target="_blank">alinas@dev.mellanox.co.il</a>&gt;</span> wrote:<br>
